      <title>东京都知事在棒球比赛中投出第一球时膝盖骨折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/tokyo-governor-breaks-knee-throwing-first-pitch-at-baseball-game</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京都知事小池百合子在养乐多燕子棒球比赛投出第一球后，球在弹向本垒的途中，她的脚在投手丘上滑倒，导致膝盖骨折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/tokyo-governor-breaks-knee-throwing-first-pitch-at-baseball-game</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 01:17:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反种族主义抗议者为英国骚乱后带来一丝喘息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/anti-racism-protesters-give-uk-some-respite-after-days-of-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数千名反种族主义抗议者出现在英国各地城镇，以对抗周三晚上未能举行的极右翼示威活动，这给这个十多年来最严重的骚乱所困扰的国家带来了一丝安慰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/anti-racism-protesters-give-uk-some-respite-after-days-of-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
